    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lamps employing incandescence as the method of illumination; may use electricity, gas, kerosene, or other means to produce the incandescence.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
